Ubuntu required dependencies:
=============================
cmake libboost-iostreams-dev libboost-date-time-dev libboost-filesystem-dev 
libboost-program-options-dev libboost-signals-dev libboost-thread-dev 
libreadline-dev libv8-dev

Ubuntu optional dependencies:
=============================
libx11-dev

Build atomd and atomic:
=======================
cd <atom root directory>
mkdir build
cd build
cmake -DUSE_PLUGIN_XORG=true ../
make

Create and install Ubuntu package: (requires cmake 2.8.3 or higher)
==================================
cd <atom root directory>
mkdir build
cd build
cpack -DUSE_PLUGIN_XORG=true ../
sudo dpkg --install Atom-1.5-x86_64.deb

Remove installed Ubuntu package:
================================
sudo dpkg --remove Atom-1.5-x86_64.deb
